AccessDeniedException.documentation: User does not have sufficient access to perform this action.

ConflictException.documentation: Updating or deleting a resource can cause an inconsistent state.

IdentityStoreDescription.documentation: This object contains basic meta information regarding an IdentityStore.

InternalServerException.documentation: Unexpected error during processing of request.

LimitExceededException.documentation: Request would cause a service limit to be exceeded.

ResourceNotFoundException.documentation: Resource (e.g. group or user) that is being requested does not exist.

ThrottlingException.documentation: Request was denied due to request throttling.

ValidationException.documentation: The input fails to satisfy the constraints.
